Privacy Policy for Vercelios
Welcome to Vercelios. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.
Collection of Your Information
We collect minimal information to provide and improve our service to you. Here's what we collect:
Project Information:
We collect project IDs to send pushes based on your preferences, along with your teamId and userId to manage your account. We don't collect any personal identifiable information like name, email, etc.
Usage Data:
This includes data like project types, deploys, build logs, redeploys, and other related usage data to help improve the functionality of Vercelios.
Use of Your Information
We use the information we collect to manage your account, process your subscriptions, improve our website, and develop new features.
Security of Your Information
We use administrative, technical, and physical security measures to protect your personal information.
Cookies and Tracking Technologies
We don't use cookies or any other tracking technologies to track users.
Third-Party Websites
Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at alberto.moral.g@gmail.com